Public Sub Clear()
&apos;&apos;&apos; Reset the current error status and clear the SF_Exception object
&apos;&apos;&apos;	Args:
&apos;&apos;&apos;	Examples:
&apos;&apos;&apos;		On Local Error GoTo Catch
&apos;&apos;&apos;		&apos;	...
